      "content": "i tried checking and my meter is giving me an error code so i cant actually see the number right now. but i really feel like i'm spiking because i feel so weird and lightheaded. if i just take 2 units of fast-acting insulin now it should probably bring me back to a normal range if i'm too high, right? i don't want to pass out.",
